00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,399
Why don't you kill him?

2
00:00:24,879 --> 00:00:25,679
You're right.

3
00:00:27,679 --> 00:00:28,480
Taking his life

4
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:29,600
would be easy.

5
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:32,159
But were he to die now,

6
00:00:33,439 --> 00:00:34,439
the best outcome is that

7
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:38,079
the Prince Duan's Residence
would merely vanish.

8
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,280
And the Shen family's grievances

9
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:42,840
would fade into oblivion

10
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:44,000
as they vanish.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,240
I want him alive.

12
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,359
To let the world see

13
00:00:49,359 --> 00:00:51,320
his hypocrisy and cruelty.

14
