♪Can one understand
what cuts to the bone♪

224
00:13:53,688 --> 00:13:55,388
♪Can one understand
what cuts to the bone♪

225
00:13:55,388 --> 00:13:59,300
♪I still cannot fathom destiny♪

226
00:13:59,488 --> 00:14:01,065
♪After countless struggles
across the waters♪

227
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:05,438
♪At last the lotus heart awakens♪

228
00:14:05,738 --> 00:14:07,738
♪Drifting across three lifetimes♪

229
00:14:07,825 --> 00:14:12,313
♪Just to wait for your
once-in-a-thousand-years glance♪

230
00:14:12,618 --> 00:14:15,458
♪The distant mountains
fade along the path home♪

231
00:14:15,938 --> 00:14:18,658
♪I walk with you through morning bells
and evening drums♪

232
00:14:19,178 --> 00:14:21,178
♪Our story lies in the mountains♪

233
